                    <app loc="line 1"><note>Ferrua (accepted doubtfully by Korhonen, who suggests also &#7936;&#947;&#959;&#961;&#945;&#963;&#943;&#945;): [&#932;&#972;&#960;&#959;&#962; &#7944;&#957;]&#948;&#961;&#941;&#959;&#965;&#903;</note></app>
